<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AudioGuideSystem PRD Standalone</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --ink: #17212b;
            --ink-soft: #5d6c7b;
            --paper: #fffaf3;
            --surface: #ffffff;
            --surface-soft: #fff5e8;
            --border: #eadfce;
            --primary: #c96a22;
            --primary-dark: #8d4410;
            --accent: #0f766e;
            --accent-soft: #e8f6f4;
            --warning: #b45309;
            --danger: #b42318;
            --success: #166534;
            --shadow: 0 18px 48px rgba(23, 33, 43, 0.12);
            --radius: 18px;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: "Segoe UI Variable", "Aptos", "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
            background:
                radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(201, 106, 34, 0.16), transparent 28%),
                radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.14), transparent 22%),
                linear-gradient(180deg, #fffdf9 0%, #fff7ef 36%, #fffdf9 100%);
            color: var(--ink);
            line-height: 1.65;
        }

        a {
            color: inherit;
        }

        nav {
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 50;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1rem;
            padding: 0.9rem 1.4rem;
            background: rgba(23, 33, 43, 0.92);
            color: white;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18);
        }

        .logo {
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: 0.02em;
            font-size: 1rem;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            list-style: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.82rem;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);
            padding: 0.35rem 0.75rem;
            border-radius: 999px;
            transition: background 0.2s ease;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
            color: white;
        }

        .hero {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 4rem 1.4rem 2.6rem;
        }

        .hero-shell {
            background:
                linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(141, 68, 16, 0.96), rgba(201, 106, 34, 0.96)),
                linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0));
            border-radius: 32px;
            color: white;
            padding: 3rem 2rem;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero-shell::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            width: 420px;
            height: 420px;
            right: -110px;
            top: -110px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16), transparent 64%);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .eyebrow {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.4rem;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
            border-radius: 999px;
            padding: 0.34rem 0.8rem;
            font-size: 0.82rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
            font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.3rem);
            line-height: 1.1;
            letter-spacing: -0.03em;
            max-width: 920px;
        }

        .hero p {
            margin: 1rem 0 0;
            max-width: 900px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
        }

        .badge-row {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 0.6rem;
            margin-top: 1.4rem;
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.35rem;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 999px;
            padding: 0.38rem 0.82rem;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
        }

        main {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 1.4rem 4rem;
        }

        section {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .section-shell {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
            border: 1px solid rgba(234, 223, 206, 0.9);
            border-radius: 28px;
            box-shadow: 0 14px 38px rgba(23, 33, 43, 0.08);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .section-head {
            padding: 1.45rem 1.5rem 1rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(234, 223, 206, 0.75);
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 245, 232, 0.95), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95));
        }

        .section-num {
            color: var(--primary);
            font-size: 0.76rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.12em;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 0.45rem;
        }

        .section-head h2 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        .section-head p {
            margin: 0.55rem 0 0;
            color: var(--ink-soft);
            max-width: 940px;
        }

        .section-body {
            padding: 1.4rem 1.5rem 1.6rem;
        }

        .stats {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .stat {
            background: var(--surface);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            padding: 1.15rem 1rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .stat .value {
            font-size: 1.95rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--primary);
            line-height: 1.05;
        }

        .stat .label {
            margin-top: 0.35rem;
            font-size: 0.82rem;
            color: var(--ink-soft);
        }

        .grid-2,
        .grid-3,
        .grid-4 {
            display: grid;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .grid-2 {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
        }

        .grid-3 {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
        }

        .grid-4 {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
        }

        .card {
            background: var(--surface);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            padding: 1.1rem 1rem;
        }

        .card h3,
        .card h4 {
            margin: 0 0 0.45rem;
            color: var(--primary-dark);
        }

        .card p,
        .card li,
        .card td,
        .card th {
            font-size: 0.92rem;
        }

        .card ul {
            margin: 0.6rem 0 0;
            padding-left: 1.1rem;
        }

        .callout {
            border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
            background: var(--accent-soft);
            border-radius: 0 16px 16px 0;
            padding: 1rem 1rem 1rem 1.1rem;
            color: #0b4d49;
        }

        .callout.warn {
            border-left-color: var(--warning);
            background: #fff4e5;
            color: #7c4a03;
        }

        .callout.danger {
            border-left-color: var(--danger);
            background: #fff0f0;
            color: #842029;
        }

        .pill-row {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 0.55rem;
        }

        .pill {
            border-radius: 999px;
            padding: 0.38rem 0.75rem;
            font-size: 0.78rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            background: #f7efe3;
            color: var(--primary-dark);
        }

        .arch {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
            gap: 0.9rem;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        .arch-box {
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 18px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff, #fff9f2);
        }

        .arch-box h3 {
            margin: 0 0 0.4rem;
        }

        .arch-box strong {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 0.45rem;
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        .diagram-panel {
            margin-top: 1rem;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 22px;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fffdf9, #fff7ef);
            padding: 1rem;
        }

        .diagram-stage {
            min-height: 280px;
            overflow: auto;
            padding: 0.4rem;
        }

        .table-wrap {
            overflow-x: auto;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 16px;
            background: white;
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            min-width: 760px;
        }

        th,
        td {
            padding: 0.78rem 0.8rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f0e7db;
            text-align: left;
            vertical-align: top;
        }

        th {
            background: #fff5e8;
            color: var(--primary-dark);
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
        }

        tr:hover td {
            background: #fffaf4;
        }

        .status {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.3rem;
            border-radius: 999px;
            padding: 0.24rem 0.65rem;
            font-size: 0.74rem;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .status.ok {
            background: #e9f7ee;
            color: var(--success);
        }

        .status.partial {
            background: #fff4e5;
            color: var(--warning);
        }

        .inventory-groups {
            display: grid;
            gap: 1.4rem;
        }

        .inventory-head {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }

        .inventory-head h3 {
            margin: 0;
        }

        .mini-meta {
            font-size: 0.82rem;
            color: var(--ink-soft);
        }

        .rules-list {
            display: grid;
            gap: 0.85rem;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        .rule {
            border: 1px dashed #d8c4ac;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 0.95rem 1rem;
            background: #fffdf9;
        }

        .rule strong {
            color: var(--primary-dark);
        }

        .sequence-toolbar {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 0.55rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .toolbar-btn,
        .seq-btn,
        .ghost-btn {
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 999px;
            padding: 0.52rem 0.95rem;
            font-size: 0.82rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            transition: transform 0.18s ease, box-shadow 0.18s ease;
        }

        .toolbar-btn,
        .seq-btn {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), #15968d);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.18);
        }

        .ghost-btn {
            background: #f7efe3;
            color: var(--primary-dark);
        }

        .toolbar-btn:hover,
        .seq-btn:hover,
        .ghost-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }

        .toolbar-btn.active {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-dark), var(--primary));
        }

        .sequence-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .sequence-card {
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff, #fffaf4);
            border-radius: 18px;
            padding: 1rem;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0.7rem;
        }

        .sequence-card h4 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--ink);
        }

        .sequence-card .idline {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 0.6rem;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 0.76rem;
            color: var(--ink-soft);
        }

        .muted {
            color: var(--ink-soft);
            font-size: 0.86rem;
        }

        .code-fallback {
            font-family: "Cascadia Code", Consolas, monospace;
            background: #1f2937;
            color: #f8fafc;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 1rem;
            overflow: auto;
            white-space: pre-wrap;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            line-height: 1.65;
        }

        .overlay {
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            background: rgba(10, 15, 20, 0.62);
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            display: none;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            z-index: 90;
            padding: 1rem;
        }

        .overlay.active {
            display: flex;
        }

        .modal {
            width: min(1140px, 96vw);
            max-height: 92vh;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 24px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 28px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.28);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .modal-head {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 1rem;
            padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-dark), var(--primary));
            color: white;
        }

        .modal-head h3 {
            margin: 0 0 0.2rem;
            font-size: 1.15rem;
        }

        .modal-head p {
            margin: 0;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            font-size: 0.88rem;
            max-width: 760px;
        }

        .close-btn {
            border: none;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
            color: white;
            width: 38px;
            height: 38px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .modal-body {
            padding: 1.2rem;
            overflow: auto;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--ink-soft);
            font-size: 0.82rem;
            padding: 1.6rem 0 0;
        }

        @media (max-width: 900px) {
            nav {
                position: static;
            }

            .nav-links {
                display: none;
            }

            .hero-shell {
                padding: 2rem 1.2rem;
            }

            .section-head,
            .section-body {
                padding-left: 1rem;
                padding-right: 1rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <nav>
        <div class="logo">AudioGuideSystem PRD</div>
        <ul class="nav-links">
            <li><a href="#overview">Tб»•ng quan</a></li>
            <li><a href="#architecture">Kiбєїn trГєc</a></li>
            <li><a href="#inventory">Chб»©c nДѓng</a></li>
            <li><a href="#rules">Quy tбєЇc</a></li>
            <li><a href="#data">Dб»Ї liб»‡u</a></li>
            <li><a href="#api">API</a></li>
            <li><a href="#sequences">Sequence</a></li>
            <li><a href="#activity-diagrams">Activity</a></li>
            <li><a href="#class-diagrams">Class</a></li>
            <li><a href="#state-diagrams">State</a></li>
            <li><a href="#gaps">KhoбєЈng trб»‘ng</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <header class="hero" id="overview">
        <div class="hero-shell">
            <div class="eyebrow">PRD tГЎi thiбєїt kбєї theo codebase thб»±c tбєї</div>
            <h1>AudioGuideSystem: PRD chi tiбєїt cho hб»‡ thб»‘ng audio tour, QR, geofence vГ  quбєЈn trб»‹ nб»™i dung du lб»‹ch</h1>
            <p>
                TГ i liб»‡u nГ y thay thбєї cГЎch kб»ѓ chuyб»‡n cЕ© trong file mбє«u bбє±ng hiб»‡n trбєЎng thбє­t cб»§a project Д‘ang cГі:
                <strong>AudioGuideAdmin</strong> lГ  CMS vбє­n hГ nh, <strong>AudioGuideAPI</strong> lГ  backend
                runtime/public API,
                vГ  <strong>AudioTourApp</strong> lГ  б»©ng dб»Ґng MAUI Android cho visitor. Mб»Ќi mГґ tбєЈ, quy tбєЇc vГ  sequence
                dЖ°б»›i Д‘Гўy Д‘б»Ѓu bГЎm theo controller,
                page, service vГ  model hiб»‡n cГі trong repo.
            </p>
            <div class="badge-row">
                <span class="badge">ASP.NET Core MVC Admin</span>
                <span class="badge">.NET 8 Web API</span>
                <span class="badge">.NET MAUI Android</span>
                <span class="badge">Geofence + Audio Queue</span>
                <span class="badge">QR Lookup + Camera Scan</span>
                <span class="badge">Shared DB + Shared Storage</span>
                <span class="badge">Session Auth cho Admin</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section id="section-overview"></section>
        <section id="section-architecture"></section>
        <section id="section-inventory"></section>
        <section id="section-rules"></section>
        <section id="section-data"></section>
        <section id="section-api"></section>
        <section id="section-sequences"></section>
        <section id="section-activity"></section>
        <section id="section-class"></section>
        <section id="section-state"></section>
        <section id="section-gaps"></section>

        <div class="footer">
            PRD standalone Д‘Ж°б»Јc dб»±ng tб»« codebase tбєЎi thб»ќi Д‘iб»ѓm hiб»‡n tбєЎi cб»§a workspace AudioGuideSystem.
        </div>
    </main>

    <div class="overlay" id="sequenceOverlay" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal">
            <div class="modal-head">
                <div>
                    <h3 id="modalTitle">Sequence</h3>
                    <p id="modalMeta">Chi tiбєїt chб»©c nДѓng</p>
                </div>
                <button class="close-btn" id="closeModal" aria-label="ДђГіng">Г—</button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <div id="modalDiagram"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script type="module">
        const architectureDefinition = `flowchart LR
    ADMIN["AudioGuideAdmin\\nASP.NET Core MVC"] -->|"CRUD nб»™i dung, media, QR, visitor"| DB[("Shared Database")]
    ADMIN -->|"Upload / delete audio, image"| FILES[("Shared Storage\\naudio, images, keys")]
    API["AudioGuideAPI\\n.NET 8 Web API"] -->|"Дђб»Ќc / ghi runtime data"| DB
    API -->|"Serve /audio vГ  /images"| FILES
    APP["AudioTourApp\\n.NET MAUI Android"] -->|"Bootstrap, map, geofence, visit, user, QR"| API
    APP -->|"Tracking GPS / audio queue / TTS"| OS["Android OS\\nLocation, Camera, TTS, Foreground Service"]
    OS -->|"Permission + location callback"| APP
    API -->|"Dashboard, analytics, tracking monitor Д‘б»Ќc sб»‘ liб»‡u giГЎn tiбєїp"| ADMIN`;

        const legacyFeatures = [
            {
                id: "M01",
                module: "Mobile App",
                title: "Bootstrap dб»Ї liб»‡u khб»џi Д‘б»™ng",
                actor: "Visitor",
                entry: "HomePage, Д‘б»•i ngГґn ngб»Ї, trЖ°б»›c khi bбє­t tracking",
                source: "MainViewModel.BootstrapAsync; ApiClient.BootstrapAsync; BootstrapController.Get",
                status: "ok",
                summary: "TбєЈi language, category, POI, tour theo ngГґn ngб»Ї hiб»‡u lб»±c; Д‘б»“ng bб»™ visitor; reset filter, map vГ  thб»­ khГґi phб»Ґc tracking.",
                mermaid: `sequenceDiagram
    participant V as Visitor
    participant APP as AudioTourApp
    participant USER as User API
    participant BOOT as Bootstrap API
    participant DB as Shared DB
    V->>APP: Mб»џ app / bбєҐm Bootstrap
    APP->>USER: POST /api/user
    USER->>DB: Upsert visitor profile
    USER-->>APP: Visitor settings
    APP->>BOOT: GET /api/bootstrap?language=...
    BOOT->>DB: Read languages, categories, POIs, tours
    BOOT-->>APP: BootstrapResponse
    APP->>APP: Normalize content, refresh map, reset filters
    APP-->>V: App sбєµn sГ ng`
            },
            {
                id: "M02",
                module: "Mobile App",
                title: "Дђб»“ng bб»™ hб»“ sЖЎ visitor",
                actor: "Visitor",
                entry: "SettingsPage / bootstrap",
                source: "MainViewModel.SyncVisitorSettingsAsync; SyncVisitorProfileAsync; UserController.Upsert",
                status: "ok",
                summary: "Дђб»“ng bб»™ display name, language, autoplay vГ  background flag giб»Їa app vб»›i server Д‘б»ѓ runtime vГ  admin nhГ¬n cГ№ng mб»™t trбєЎng thГЎi.",
                mermaid: `sequenceDiagram
    participant V as Visitor
    participant APP as SettingsPage
    participant VM as MainViewModel
    participant API as User API
    participant DB as Visitors
    V->>APP: Дђб»•i tГЄn / autoplay / background
    APP->>VM: SyncVisitorSettingsAsync()
    VM->>API: POST /api/user
    API->>DB: Create or update visitor
    API-->>VM: VisitorProfile
    VM->>VM: Apply server flags
    VM-->>V: Hiб»ѓn thб»‹ trбєЎng thГЎi Д‘ГЈ Д‘б»“ng bб»™`
            },
            {
                id: "M03",
                module: "Mobile App",
                title: "Xin vГ  kiб»ѓm tra quyб»Ѓn tracking",
                actor: "Visitor",
                entry: "SettingsPage",
                source: "RequestTrackingPermissionsAsync; AppPermissionService.RequestTrackingPermissionsAsync",
                status: "ok",
                summary: "App xin quyб»Ѓn GPS khi dГ№ng app, GPS nб»Ѓn vГ  notification Д‘б»ѓ sбєµn sГ ng cho tracking + foreground service.",
                mermaid: `sequenceDiagram
    participant V as Visitor
    participant APP as AudioTourApp
    participant PERM as AppPermissionService
    participant OS as Android Permissions
    V->>APP: BбєҐm cбєҐp quyб»Ѓn tracking
    APP->>PERM: RequestTrackingPermissionsAsync()
    PERM->>OS: Request location when in use
    PERM->>OS: Request location always
    PERM->>OS: Request notifications
    OS-->>PERM: Permission status
    PERM-->>APP: AppPermissionSnapshot
    APP-->>V: Hiб»ѓn thб»‹ trбєЎng thГЎi GPS/background/noti`
            },
            {
                id: "M04",
                module: "Mobile App",
                title: "Xin vГ  kiб»ѓm tra quyб»Ѓn camera",
                actor: "Visitor",
                entry: "SettingsPage hoбє·c QrScannerPage",
                source: "RequestCameraPermissionAsync; AppPermissionService.RequestCameraPermissionAsync",
                status: "ok",
