    note right of APP: Pha 1: Дђб»“ng bб»™ dб»Ї liб»‡u (Bootstrap)
    APP->>BOOT: GET /api/bootstrap?language={lang}
    BOOT->>DB: Truy vбєҐn danh sГЎch POI, Tour Д‘ang active
