    end
    
    rect rgb(255, 240, 245)
    note right of APP: Pha 2: CбєҐp quyб»Ѓn & Theo dГµi vб»‹ trГ­
    APP->>OS: YГЄu cбє§u quyб»Ѓn Vб»‹ trГ­ (Location Permission)
    
    alt Bб»‹ tб»« chб»‘i (Denied)
        OS-->>APP: Permission Denied
        APP-->>V: CбєЈnh bГЎo: "б»Ёng dб»Ґng cбє§n quyб»Ѓn vб»‹ trГ­ Д‘б»ѓ hoбєЎt Д‘б»™ng"
    else ДђЖ°б»Јc cбєҐp (Granted)
        OS-->>APP: Permission Granted
        APP->>OS: Khб»џi Д‘б»™ng Foreground Service bбєЇt GPS
        
