            document.getElementById("section-rules").innerHTML = `
                <div class="section-shell" id="rules">
                    <div class="section-head">
                        <div class="section-num">Section 04</div>
                        <h2>Quy tбєЇc nghiб»‡p vб»Ґ quan trб»Ќng</h2>
                        <p>ДђГўy lГ  nhб»Їng rule cГі бєЈnh hЖ°б»џng trб»±c tiбєїp tб»›i thiбєїt kбєї sбєЈn phбє©m, cбєЈm nhбє­n visitor vГ  cГЎch Д‘б»™i vбє­n hГ nh nhбє­p dб»Ї liб»‡u.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="section-body">
                        <div class="rules-list">
                            <div class="rule"><strong>Bootstrap theo ngГґn ngб»Ї hiб»‡u lб»±c</strong>: App dГ№ng ngГґn ngб»Ї Д‘ang chб»Ќn, nhЖ°ng nбєїu User API trбєЈ vб»Ѓ visitor cГі language khГЎc thГ¬ bootstrap lбєҐy language hiб»‡u lб»±c tб»« visitor.</div>
                            <div class="rule"><strong>POI runtime phбєЈi active</strong>: Chб»‰ POI <code>IsActive = true</code> mб»›i vГ o bootstrap, map feed, nearby vГ  geofence.</div>
                            <div class="rule"><strong>Translation runtime chб»‰ lбєҐy bбєЈn published</strong>: Runtime API include translation cГі <code>IsPublished = true</code> rб»“i chб»Ќn bбєЈn phГ№ hб»Јp vб»›i request language.</div>
                            <div class="rule"><strong>TriggerMode quyбєїt Д‘б»‹nh cГЎch kГ­ch hoбєЎt</strong>: <code>enter</code>, <code>nearby</code>, <code>manual</code>, <code>both</code> Д‘Ж°б»Јc xГ©t б»џ server geofence vГ  local app state.</div>
                            <div class="rule"><strong>Chб»‘ng phГЎt lбє·p hai lб»›p</strong>: Server dГ№ng <code>GeofenceTriggers</code> Д‘б»ѓ kiб»ѓm tra cooldown/debounce; app cГІn cГі bб»™ nhб»› local Д‘б»ѓ chбє·n lбє·p thГЄm.</div>
                            <div class="rule"><strong>Audio mode cГі thб»© tб»± Ж°u tiГЄn</strong>: Nбєїu POI lГ  <code>audio</code> hoбє·c <code>audio-priority</code> vГ  cГі file thГ¬ app thб»­ audio trЖ°б»›c; nбєїu khГґng thГ¬ Д‘б»Ќc TTS trЖ°б»›c rб»“i mб»›i fallback audio.</div>
                            <div class="rule"><strong>Visit history Д‘Ж°б»Јc normalize tб»± Д‘б»™ng</strong>: API visit sбєЅ tб»± suy ra StartTime, EndTime, Duration nбєїu client gб»­i thiбєїu mб»™t phбє§n dб»Ї liб»‡u.</div>
                            <div class="rule"><strong>Tour stop phб»Ґ thuб»™c SortOrder</strong>: Mб»—i stop cГі thб»© tб»± duy nhбєҐt theo <code>(TourId, SortOrder)</code> vГ  mobile phГЎt tuбє§n tб»± theo danh sГЎch Д‘ГЈ sort.</div>
                            <div class="rule"><strong>Language vГ  category cГі rГ ng buб»™c xГіa</strong>: KhГґng xГіa Д‘Ж°б»Јc language Д‘ang dГ№ng trong POI/translation; khГґng xГіa Д‘Ж°б»Јc category Д‘ang Д‘Ж°б»Јc POI tham chiбєїu.</div>
                            <div class="rule"><strong>QR code lГ  duy nhбєҐt</strong>: QR phбєЈi unique toГ n hб»‡ thб»‘ng; batch bus stop sбєЅ map keyword tГЄn Д‘iб»ѓm dб»«ng sang POI phГ№ hб»Јp rб»“i tбєЎo hoбє·c update code chuбє©n.</div>
                            <div class="rule"><strong>Visitor profile tб»« server cГі quyб»Ѓn override app</strong>: Cб»ќ <code>AllowAutoPlay</code> vГ  <code>AllowBackgroundTracking</code> lЖ°u б»џ visitor profile cГі thб»ѓ lГ m app chбє·n autoplay hoбє·c dб»«ng tracking khi ra background.</div>
                            <div class="rule"><strong>Admin session bбєЈo vб»‡ toГ n bб»™ route ngoГ i Auth</strong>: Middleware session chбє·n truy cбє­p mб»Ќi mГ n hГ¬nh khГЎc nбєїu chЖ°a cГі session <code>user</code>, timeout mбє·c Д‘б»‹nh 8 giб»ќ.</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="grid-2" style="margin-top:1rem;">
                            <div class="callout"><strong>Assumption vбє­n hГ nh</strong><br>POI phбєЈi cГі tб»Ќa Д‘б»™ chuбє©n, radius hб»Јp lГЅ vГ  nб»™i dung Д‘б»§ tб»‘t thГ¬ geofence + audio mб»›i Д‘em lбєЎi trбєЈi nghiб»‡m tб»± nhiГЄn. ChбєҐt lЖ°б»Јng dб»Ї liб»‡u quyбєїt Д‘б»‹nh chбєҐt lЖ°б»Јng trбєЈi nghiб»‡m.</div>
                            <div class="callout warn"><strong>Assumption kб»№ thuбє­t</strong><br>Tracking hiб»‡n nghiГЄng vб»Ѓ Android foreground/foreground-service. Nбєїu muб»‘n production cб»©ng hЖЎn cбє§n thГЄm hardening cho background execution, permission handling vГ  failure telemetry.</div>
