                        <h2>API capability matrix</h2>
                        <p>Phбє§n nГ y gom toГ n bб»™ API runtime/public theo nhГіm nghiб»‡p vб»Ґ Д‘б»ѓ PO, BA hoбє·c dev Д‘б»Ѓu cГі thб»ѓ trace tб»« chб»©c nДѓng sang endpoint thбє­t.</p>
